Day 40: Docker EXEC Operations

Date: October 6, 2025
Overview
Executed commands inside running containers.
Key Concepts Learned

Docker exec command
Interactive vs non-interactive execution
Running processes in containers
Debugging running containers

Commands Used
bashdocker exec -it container_name bash
docker exec container_name ls -la
docker exec -d container_name service nginx restart
Challenges Faced
Understanding when to use interactive mode (-it) vs detached mode (-d).
